A '''Neuvian sundae''' was an immense dessert from the [[Neuvia system/Legends|Neuvia system]]. It consisted of frozen cream and fruit and was served in a wide bowl. [[Dex's Diner/Legends|Dex's Diner]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] served them for 2.7 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] where they consisted of two scoops of [[Denta bean ice cream]] and a choice of [[Trammistan chocolate]] or [[zoochberry topping]] as well as atomically-aerated [[Cream/Legends|cream]] and a [[zherry]].<ref name="Dining at Dex's">{{Hyperspace|url=fans/hyperspace/source/dexdiner/index.html|text=Dining at Dex's|int=Dining at Dex's}}</ref> They were also served on a [[Sooman starship]] through a [[Food synthesizer/Legends|food synthesizer]], which the [[Alzarian/Legends|Alzarian]] [[Prince/Legends|prince]] [[Plooz]] took a liking too as he was being transported from [[Sooma]] to [[Alzar]].<ref name="Droids 4">[[Droids (1986) 4|''Droids'' (1986) 4]]</ref>

